OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe odd
OL,6,Flight coastal shower is possible
OL,7,Fovernight. Otherwise, dry with clear
OL,8,Fspells and light winds. This will
OL,9,Fallow temperatures to fall away and a
OL,10,Fpatchy frost to form.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA dry, bright and chilly
OL,13,Fstart. Remaining mostly dry with cloud
OL,14,Fincreasing from the west. Some light
OL,15,Frain is possible in the west by
OL,16,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
