OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSome
OL,6,Fshowers possible on Sunday. Cloudy on
OL,7,FMonday with some rain. This turning
OL,8,Fheavy overnight. Rather wet and windy
OL,9,Fon Tuesday. Temperatures slowly
OL,10,Fincreasing near to average.
